Paladin of Conquest
---

(managed to clear the sheet for this one... will rewrite later)

Uses the Unearthed Arcana Oath of Conquest found here : http://media.wizards.com/2017/dnd/downloads/June5UA_RevisedClassOptv1.pdf

Background for Noble -- Knight grants you three retainer followers that will assist you as servants, but not in combat.


Fighting Style -- Great Weapon Master
May reroll 1's and 2's on damage dice with a two-handed or versatile weapon (such as your polearm)

Polearm Master Feat:
Allows you to make Attacks of Opportunity on enemies when they move within your reach from outside.
May use a bonus action when you make an attack to also attack with the opposite end of the weapon for 1d4 bludgeoning damage.